OL,3,CMurder victim's organs save lives of
OL,4,Cfive others
OL,6,FThe mother of a murder victim said it
OL,7,Fis "comforting" to know that he has
OL,8,Fhelped to save five other lives after
OL,9,Fdonating his organs.
OL,11,FAdi Whiting, 35, was attacked with a
OL,12,Fbaseball bat outside the pub in
OL,13,FBoston, Lincolnshire, where he worked
OL,14,Fas a barman.
OL,16,FHe died 10 days after the incident in
OL,17,FJanuary.
