OL,3,CMurder victim's organs save lives of
OL,4,Cfive others
OL,6,FFive people received his lungs, heart,
OL,7,Fliver and kidneys. His pancreas and
OL,8,Fbrain were also used to support life-
OL,9,Fsaving research.
OL,11,FMr Whiting's mother Debbie Paul said
OL,12,Fit was an easy decision to donate his
OL,13,Forgans.
OL,15,FMrs Paul said: "Adi was one of those
OL,16,Fpeople who was always helping others.
