OL,3,CMurder victim's organs save lives of
OL,4,Cfive others
OL,6,F"I find it comforting to know that
OL,7,Fpart of Adi is out there, and I am so
OL,8,Fpleased that five people have
OL,9,Fbenefited and have got the chance to
OL,10,Fhave a decent life.
OL,12,F"It was not a hard decision for us to
OL,13,Fmake, in fact I feel it was a very
OL,14,Fgood one, because we knew what Adi
OL,15,Fwanted."
OL,17,FMr Whiting was fatally injured after
OL,18,Fintervening when he saw a couple
OL,19,Farguing outside the Carpenters Arms in
OL,20,FBoston on 14 January.
