OL,3,CMurder victim's organs save lives of
OL,4,Cfive others
OL,6,FA 36-year-old man was later convicted
OL,7,Fof murder. He will be sentenced next
OL,8,Fmonth.
OL,10,FMrs Paul said: "When we were told that
OL,11,Fthere was only a very small chance
OL,12,Fthat Adi might pull through I remember
OL,13,Fsaying to the doctor that he would
OL,14,Fwant to donate his organs."
OL,16,FBoston, Grantham and Lincoln's
OL,17,Fhospitals will be illuminated every
OL,18,Fevening this week for Organ Donation
OL,19,FWeek.
