OL,3,CMurder victim's organs save lives of
OL,4,Cfive others
OL,6,FAccording to NHS Blood and Transplant,
OL,7,Fmore than 7,600 people are waiting for
OL,8,Fan organ.
OL,10,FAnthony Clarkson, of NHS Blood and
OL,11,FTransplant, said: "Every day across
OL,12,Fthe UK thousands of patients and their
OL,13,Ffamilies are waiting for a life-saving
OL,14,Fcall. But this can often only happen
OL,15,Fas a result of another family
OL,16,Freceiving very difficult news and
OL,17,Fsupporting organ donation to help
OL,18,Fothers."
